Computational Reactor Command Architecture
│
├── Strategic Oversight Layer
│   ├── Governance & Policy Control
│   │   ├── Regulatory Compliance Engine
│   │   └── Risk Mitigation Strategy Controller
│   └── Mission Planning & Prioritization
│       ├── Simulation Objective Generator
│       └── Multi-Domain Task Scheduler
│
├── Operational Command Layer
│   ├── Reactor Domain Control Units
│   │   ├── Nuclear Reactor Coordination Node
│   │   ├── Chemical Reactor Coordination Node
│   │   ├── Biological Reactor Coordination Node
│   │   └── Medical Reactor Coordination Node
│   ├── Resource Orchestration Manager
│   │   ├── Compute Resource Allocator
│   │   └── Data Throughput Optimizer
│   └── Model Execution Command Hub
│       ├── Scenario Initialization Handler
│       └── Execution Progress Tracker
│
├── Tactical Execution Layer
│   ├── Simulation & Modeling Engine
│   │   ├── Reaction Kinetics Solver
│   │   ├── CFD (Computational Fluid Dynamics) Core
│   │   ├── Thermal Transfer Module
│   │   └── Multi-Scale Integration Engine
│   ├── Data Acquisition & Preprocessing Unit
│   │   ├── Sensor Fusion & Virtualization
│   │   └── Experimental Data Translator
│   └── AI/ML Decision Support Kernel
│       ├── Predictive Analytics Module
│       └── Anomaly Detection Subsystem
│
└── Feedback & Adaptation Layer
    ├── Performance Assessment Interface
    │   ├── KPI Comparator
    │   └── Scenario Benchmark Evaluator
    ├── Adaptive Learning Loop
    │   ├── Parameter Retuning System
    │   └── Model Refinement Protocol
    └── Command Update Dispatcher
        └── Real-Time Doctrine Adjuster
